{"tid":1692250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"添馬公園未示威先清場","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T03:54:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61eba2be5812704a32ae0449acbe98be54e5499a","tid":1692250,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:54:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/FBGMCZZ47HHP76E7SUKBCH3P3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FFBGMCZZ47HHP76E7SUKBCH3P3Q%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=8e846b2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FFBGMCZZ47HHP76E7SUKBCH3P3Q%2F&h=06dc0be8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/FBGMCZZ47HHP76E7SUKBCH3P3Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n添馬公園未示威先清場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/u8yHNHPXrCBcqV4XQQ4QjoIUpgA=/802x455/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/WB4Z755YSJJSSOHFLCN5ICEEGM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fu8yHNHPXrCBcqV4XQQ4QjoIUpgA%3D%2F802x455%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FWB4Z755YSJJSSOHFLCN5ICEEGM.gif&h=4f84359d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名年輕人坐在草地看書，遭防暴警驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網民昨發起七區集會，當中添馬公園接近政府機關，警方嚴陣以待，中午前已用水馬封鎖立法會出入口，又在海富天橋設立防線，連立法會議員馬逢國途經亦被警員截查，一批防暴警下午則改往公園清場，有巿民不滿無故被驅散，斥警察無法無天。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：立場記者被扣手銬拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國遭警截查<br />\n<br />\n有網民號召昨下午1時到添馬公園集會，現場所見，園內只有外傭及公公婆婆，及零星年輕人坐在草地看書，身上沒有裝備或口罩；警方下午2時突廣播指「添馬公園將可能有示威活動，在場市民請立即離開」，又派出30名防暴警驅散巿民。<br />\n<br />\n有手持枴杖的婆婆上前與防暴警員理論，銀髮族方先生斥警方清場行為無理：「佢根本唔搵理由，叫你走咪走囉，𠵱家香港嚟講，實質係無政府狀態，如果有政府，可唔可以畀呢啲事發生呢？」他又不滿說：「呢度公園，公眾地方，禮拜日我嚟坐吓，吸吓海風，唔係好奇怪啫，好似噚日維園，有菲傭有印傭，唔通佢哋又係去示威咩？」<br />\n<br />\n警方在立法會對開採取嚴密佈防，以水馬及鐵欄圍封出入口及天橋，立法會議員馬逢國沿海富天橋步行前往立法會期間，遭防暴警截查，還遭警員問他是否一定要前往立法會，有總督察上前認出馬逢國，才讓他離開。<br />\n<br />\n■記者文兆麟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/NA6yiRdULMZavPCiO9JW9OyaWFE=/802x401/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/INGNINH3N6WDZ66DZAZMQARL7Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FNA6yiRdULMZavPCiO9JW9OyaWFE%3D%2F802x401%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FINGNINH3N6WDZ66DZAZMQARL7Y.gif&h=e4210a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬逢國途經海富天橋時被警員截查。<br />\nAppleDaily"}]}